# Privacy and Terms — Keep In-App and Web in Sync

When editing **Privacy Policy** or **Terms of Use** content, update **both** places so the app and the App Store / public links stay in sync:

- **Web (App Store, GitHub Pages):** `docs/privacy.html` and `docs/terms.html`
- **In-app views:** `ios/App/App/Views/PrivacyView.swift` and `ios/App/App/Views/TermsView.swift`

If you change copy, sections, or "Last updated" in one place, apply the same changes to the other. See `docs/README.md` for the same reminder.
